SUMMARY:Spring Serenity Walk
DESCRIPTION:Join TLC for a beautiful morning at Flower Hill!\nImmerse yourself in the tranquility of a spring walk and listen for the arrival of migrating birds. Along the way we will observe the native wildflowers that are blooming\, especially the rare Catawba Rhododendrons. Feel the soft breezes that embrace you and enjoy the beauty of spring on this slow one-mile walk. This is a free event but preregistration is required.\n\n\n\nIf registration is full\, please fill out the waitlist form here by April 20th at noon.
URL:https://triangleland.org/event/spring-serenity-walk
LOCATION:Flower Hill Nature Preserve\, 9038 Flower Hill Rd\, Middlesex\, NC\, 27557\, United States
ORGANIZER;CN="Amaya Horner":MAILTO:ahorner@triangleland.org
END:VEVENT
